—Ton̈ jilaꞌ ebnaj juẍta bey yul hunun con̈ob bayxaticꞌa con̈ecꞌ jalaꞌ Istzotiꞌ Comam, cat jilni hanicꞌ ye ebnaj, ẍi naj Pablo tuꞌ.
—Haꞌ ebnaj Israel tiꞌ, caw ton̈e chihul ebnaj yakꞌaꞌ somchahoꞌcan̈ isnabal sunil jet con̈ob tiꞌ.
