Mach yilalo ay tzet chꞌakꞌlax tet huneꞌ Dios tuꞌ yu anma. Wal xin haꞌ Comam chꞌakꞌni cocawil cosunil, haꞌ Comam chꞌakꞌnipaxo jakꞌekꞌ cohikꞌaꞌ, yeb sunil tzet ayon̈.
